  "texts": [
    "Finally [39][40], underscore the emerging synergies between Large Language Models and traditional machine learning methods, particularly in the realm of e-commerce recommendations.",
    "EXPERIMENTS 4.1 DatasetsThe dataset provided comprises essential physical and chemical attributes of Li-ion silicate cathodes, crucial for predicting the class of a Li-ion battery.",
    "These batteries are classified based on their crystal system, which includes three primary categories: monoclinic, orthorhombic, and triclinic.",
    "The dataset features include 'Formation Energy (eV)', 'E Above Hull (eV)', 'Band Gap (eV)', 'Nsites', 'Density (gm/cc)', 'Volume', Formula', 'Spacegroup', 'Has Bandstructure'.",
    "Split into training and test sets in an 8:2 ratio, this dataset offers a comprehensive foundation for developing predictive models to classify Li-ion battery crystal systems, facilitating advancements in energy storage technology."
  ]
}